{"tid":1455514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌，就算你話我係散水黨，我都係要講，機場嘅快D走！！","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:25:29.000Z","uid":295304,"like":97,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"caf997611ca869d09e28025a9cd31468d0a1064f","tid":1455514,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:05:14.000Z","msg":"唉屌，我知我P牌，講完可能會被人話帶風向<br />\n未試過咁嬲自己以前上連登淨係睇，唔申請account<br />\n但真係唔講唔得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但真係好認真咁對機場嘅各位講，真係要走！<br />\n尤其係喺入黑後真係唔好留！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzp9MXS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftzp9MXS.jpg&h=28dcfd12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭先我睇人哋send出黎既資料，<br />\n機場已經係取消定之後嘅航班，等機場冇哂旅客就可以做野，而且d狗都已經帶埋黑旗去，真係唔好留！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為今次大家打算和平靜坐，有好多係冇帶gear去，佢如果出催淚彈、開槍、打人，真係會好嚴重！<br />\n（另外想問下機場如果夜晚斷電，咁嗰度係咪會全黑，呢樣我唔肯定、想問下其他巴打絲打）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家真係唔好留！唔係咩散水黨，係好認真！<br />\n我唔明點解明明知道越黎越多狗入咗去機場，而且機場已經清定場，大部分人又冇帶gear入去，點解都仲叫人留？？而家D狗明明都已經唔打算再理法例、再講道理，仲話靜坐唔會被人拉？<br />\n仲記唔記得何式凝嗰次，天水圍點樣一次過俾人拉哂？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">不過雖然我話要散，但散嘅話，唔好獨留一堆<br />\n而且最危險嘅情況係，一堆勸走、一堆勸留，到時走嘅人走咗，但留嗰批繼續留，人少得制，會更加大獲！<br />\n如果走嘅話，抬都抬埋佢哋走（但小心係鬼唔走）</span>"},{"pid":"45749d8d9ec7270a461a150d5fd882953ededa02","tid":1455514,"uid":168250,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:05:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">可以建議 但係由前線決定</span></span>"},{"pid":"cb064037dbbe634782ec4b502d7938442710865b","tid":1455514,"uid":32861,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:05:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2019仲留守任何地方？<br />\n<br />\n要守既只有一個地方-香港<br />\n<br />\n2014仲留守唔夠咩？</span>"},{"pid":"a4bf70c8ff0594b03daf15f8fced288d3697d0e5","tid":1455514,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6738f8dca489c068c4570da7194bc35fcbc227c5","tid":1455514,"uid":295304,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:07:24.000Z","msg":"自推100次<br />\n我唔想唔講之後後悔"},{"pid":"93ef76bed893ba5b7b47740e4be9f131ef9521b3","tid":1455514,"uid":81008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"小心"},{"pid":"ef1de8ea5f684071fc9608421c5b1c5a94be7f2f","tid":1455514,"uid":190541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:08:36.000Z","msg":"快走"},{"pid":"dc8bd0ec3f5cf991a9a246d95749d1e418294b40","tid":1455514,"uid":295304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:08:58.000Z","msg":"我知道係要由佢哋自己決定<br />\n但真係越諗越驚，好怕會出事"},{"pid":"1da6502e245d97c38faf1d67ea2c345b3678d810","tid":1455514,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:09:54.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"e9aedce58efdfba35279f3ad4d0b7d809e3d7739","tid":1455514,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:10:04.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"558d4e531d43d8baa50d4d7df15a00d398aed36b","tid":1455514,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:10:22.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"f9a60eb6cc4078205e4b84f7dd4c3a805025b168","tid":1455514,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:11:13.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"338ae5fc1c3075f27b80c4d80e572fab7a1fddb3","tid":1455514,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:12:17.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"b18b8261bb998074f8d92cf6e3b66ef5e3e7bd1e","tid":1455514,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:13:39.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"b1839997aeb2f8ac95f33917b9c4d6e44d6fad89","tid":1455514,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit